        <description>9. **Set 'Assignment Group' Based on Category**  &#13;
   If the **Category** is set to "Inquiry/Help," automatically set the **Assignment Group** to "Service Desk" in the Incident form.</description>
        <field>u_category</field>
        <global>true</global>
        <isolate_script>true</isolate_script>
        <messages/>
        <name>Set Assignment Group for Inquiry</name>
        <order/>
        <script><![CDATA[function onChange(control, oldValue, newValue, isLoading, isTemplate) {
   // Ensure the form is not loading and the new value is not empty
   if (isLoading || newValue === '') {
      return;
   }

   // Check if the category is set to "Inquiry"
   if (g_form.getValue('u_category') === 'inquiry') {
      // Set the Assignment Group to "Service Desk"
      g_form.setValue('u_assignment_group', 'd625dccec0a8016700a222a0f7900d06');
   } else {
      // If category is not "Inquiry", clear the Assignment Group
      g_form.setValue('u_assignment_group', '');
   }
}
]]></script>
